      • createCompatibility

        Compatibility createCompatibility​(String id,
                                  String resourceName,
                                  Version resourceVersion,
                                  String baseName,
                                  Version baseVersion,
                                  Difference diffValue,
                                  List<Diff> diffValues,
                                  Contract contract)
        Factory method for complete initialization of Compatibility implementation.
        Parameters:
        id - unique id
        resourceName - compared resource name (crce.identity)
        resourceVersion - compared resource version in OSGi representation
        baseName - name of the resource used as base
        baseVersion - OSGi representation of the version of the resource used as base
        diffValue - aggregated difference value of the two resources
        diffValues - complete diff of the two resources
        contract - contract the instance is related to
        Returns:
        new Compatibility instance

      • createCompatibility

        Compatibility createCompatibility​(String id,
                                  String resourceName,
                                  Version resourceVersion,
                                  Version baseVersion,
                                  Difference diffValue,
                                  List<Diff> diffValues,
                                  Contract contract)
        Factory method for complete initialization of Compatibility implementation. Base name is set to the same value as resource name.
        Parameters:
        id - unique id
        resourceName - compared resource name (crce.identity)
        resourceVersion - compared resource version in OSGi representation
        baseVersion - OSGi representation of the version of the resource used as base
        diffValue - aggregated difference value of the two resources
        diffValues - complete diff of the two resources
        contract - contract the instance is related to
        Returns:
        new Compatibility instance
